title: Ep. #99 | Celebratory Break-Up Songs: 2NE1, Jennie, DEAN
description:
Break-ups are not always so blue. In this episode, Eric gathers the best happy break-up songs that remind us that parting ways with our ex-lovers can call for some celebration.
